 This is for the best, Twitter. I was never fully comfortable with your character limits. And you deserve more than the occasional tweet.
 Twitter, it's me. I want run-on sentences. I want to hear falling intonations. I want my 20/25 vision and my midday productivity back.
 Twitter, we've had some great times together but it's time for me to move on. It's not you -you're informative, fun and always there for me.
